channel.title: Interleaved RSS Feed
channel.description: This is an interleaved feed of the most recent entries from each RSS source, skipping any feeds with errors.

item.title: Are Stock Markets Rallying in Anticipation of a Trump Victory?
Union leader's provocative RNC speech draws ire from some in organized labor
item.description: Teamster President Sean O'Brien's speech at the Republican National Convention has drawn backlash from both the union and its critics, who view his move as "two-faced."

item.title: Schumer to Sen. Menendez: Resign After Conviction
item.description: Senate Majority Leader Chuck Schumer called on Sen. Bob Menendez, D-N.J., to resign on Tuesday after Menendez's conviction on all criminal counts he faced at a corruption trial.

item.title: WATCH: Leaked Call Between Trump and RFK Jr. Demonstrates Civil Dialogue Despite Some Disagreements
Schumer calls for Democrat Menendez's resignation after guilty verdict
item.description: Senate Majority Leader Chuck Schumer called for Bob Menendez to resign as New Jersey senator on Tuesday after he was found guilty.

item.title: Ohio Dem Rep. Greg Landsman Backs Off Call to Oust Biden
item.description: Rep. Greg Landsman, D-Ohio, has given up on publicly calling for President Joe Biden to drop out of the 2024 presidential race.

item.title: 'Staged Theatrics to Get the Votes of Idiots': Clownish Professor Declares Trump Shooting 'Faked'
GOP lawsuit targets alleged Biden 'weaponizing' of voter registration: 'Democratic turnout machine'
item.description: A GOP lawsuit seeks to block President Biden's effort to register 3.5 million voters, arguing the White House is "weaponizing" government.

item.title: RFK Jr Apologizes After Video of Call With Trump Leaks
item.description: Robert F. Kennedy Jr., running a third-party campaign for president, has apologized after video of a call he had Monday with former President Donald Trump leaked.

item.title: On The Scene at The RNC - Recap and Thoughts From a First-Time Alternate Delegate
JD Vance on 2024 ticket could help Republicans in 'vulnerable Rust Belt states' this election cycle: experts
item.description: Sen. JD Vance, former President Trump's 2024 running mate, could have more of an impact on swing state races than in his own state of Ohio, according to strategists.

item.title: Trump Attorney Blanche: DOJ Should Drop Prosecutions
item.description: Donald Trump's lead counsel in multiple criminal cases says President Joe Biden or Attorney General Merrick Garland should end the ongoing prosecutions against the former president following the Supreme Court's recent presidential immunity ruling.

item.title: Beards and Politics: Why JD Vance's Beard Must Never Be Shaven
Video shows moment Secret Service agents tossed Trump's shoes offstage
item.description: A new video angle from the assassination attempt against former President Donald Trump shows Secret Service agents tossing his shoes off-stage before moving him to safety.

item.title: Delegate Reaction to Trump's VP Pick: 'We Love J.D.!'
item.description: Once Donald Trump announced his choice of Ohio Sen. J.D. Vance as his vice-presidential running mate Monday afternoon, delegates to the Republican National Convention responded immediately-almost all of them with approval.
